high_descs: Walk forward turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, pick up the white coffee cup to the right of the lettuce.
Turn around to face the red microwave.
Open the microwave door, let the apple roll out of the microwave. Place the coffee cup inside, close the door.  Open the microwave door to pick up the coffee cup. Close the microwave door.
Turn around, walk forward, turn to the left to face the coffee machine.
Place the coffee cup under the spout of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Move a coffee cup from the refrigerator to the coffee machine.

high_descs: walk straight, turn left, walk to the refrigerator
take the cup out of the refrigerator, close the refrigerator
turn around, turn around to the microwave
open the microwave, put the cup in, heat the cup, take the cup out
turn right to the coffee machine
put the cup in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: heat the cup with microwave, put the cup in the coffee machine

high_descs: Take two steps forward, turn left, walk to the fridge.
Take the coffee cup off of the bottom shelf in the fridge.
Take a step to the right, stand in front of the microwave.
Place the coffee cup in the microwave, heat up the coffee cup for a few seconds, take the coffee cup out of the microwave.
Turn around, walk to the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated coffee cup on the coffee maker.
